name: Far From Home (TheZBillDyl, Leah, WesMcW, Zaidis)
name_original: Far From Home (TheZBillDyl, Leah, WesMcW, Zaidis)
description:
Game Description Lost in the woods. Alone in the dark. Where did you wander to? You are Charles, a young boy who was playing in the woods during the day and got lost. Not only that but, you lost the key to your house too! The sun is going down and night time is approaching! You must find the keys you dropped and get back home! The task is easier said than done though.... There are things that lurk in the darkness. Credits
